                        <interp inst="t18641024-953-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.—<hi rend="italic">He was further charged with having been before convicted, in July</hi>, 1863, <hi rend="italic">
when he was sentenced to One Years' Imprisonment; to which he</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
PLEADED GUILTY</hi>.*—<hi rend="italic">
